headline.main: Soccer: Wenger Rejects 'Completely False' Reports of Sanchez Bust-Up
headline.print_headline: Soccer: Wenger Rejects 'Completely False' Reports of Sanchez Bust-Up

lead_paragraph: Reports of a training ground bust-up between Chilean forward Alexis Sanchez and his Arsenal team mates are "completely false", manager Arsene Wenger said on Monday.
